(26,106747,NULL,'2024-06-18 09:52:59','2024-08-12 14:53:40','{\"id\":106747,\"name\":\"G19\",\"title\":\"\",\"description\":\"Điền từ còn thiếu vào ô trống\",\"duration\":0,\"platform\":{\"id\":391,\"description\":\"Đoạn văn - Điền vào chỗ trống\",\"code\":\"19\",\"isActive\":true,\"createdAt\":\"2024-06-11T18:00:30.000Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-06-13T19:06:04.000Z\"},\"skill\":\"WRITING\",\"content\":{\"text\":\"<p>My mother is a person I admire most. She devoted a lot of time and energy to the upbringing of my two brothers and 1. Despite working hard, she always made time to teach us many useful things which are necessary and  important in our later lives. Moreover, she is a good role model for me to  follow. She always tries to get on well with people who live next door and  help everyone when they are in  difficulties, so most of them respect  and love her. I admire and look up to  my mother because she not only  brings me up well but also stands by  me and gives some help if necessary. For example, when I encounter some  difficulties, she will give me some  precious advice to help me solve those  problems. She has a major influence  on me and 1 hope that I will inherit  some of her traits.</p>\"},\"hint\":{\"text\":\"<p>Không có đâu sói ạ !!</p>\"},\"answerHelp\":{\"text\":null},\"subQuestions\":[{\"content\":{\"bot\":null,\"title\":\"Complete the  bellow .Choose one or two word from the passage for each answer\",\"text\":\"My mother is a [...] I admire most. She devoted a lot of time and [...] to the upbringing of my two brothers and Despite [...] hard, she  always made time to teach us many useful things.\",\"vnTitle\":\"\",\"pronunciation\":\"\",\"image\":null,\"audio\":null,\"video\":null},\"explanation\":{\"text\":\"Không có đâu =))\"},\"message\":{\"correct\":\"<p>Bravo</p>\",\"wrong\":\"<p>Nooooo</p>\"},\"answers\":[{\"text\":\"person\",\"pronunciation\":\"\",\"vnTitle\":\"\",\"timeout\":0,\"position\":1,\"image\":null,\"audio\":null,\"rightResponse\":\"1\